Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 542 m) and pressure (up 9 mbar).

The past week and month had observable variation in feels like temperature (up 38.7°C), outside temperature (up 40.9°C), dew point temperature (up 36.0°C), and cloud levels (up 949 m) when compared to today.
